elements.name: [CypressCoverage] account enrollment and automatic linking from intermediary mode

steps.name: I enter the Social Manager Section
The Social Login section has loaded, click on the second button that contains the text "Continuar con Google"
The google authentication section loads
I type the "<gmail>" in the "Correo electronico" field and the "<Password>" in the "Contrasena" field
I click on the "Ingresar" button
Loads the "Tu correo electrónico de Gmail no está asociado a una cuenta lifemiles" modal
I click on the "crea tu cuenta" link
Loads the view "Crea tu cuenta" social enrollment Step 1
The "<gmail>" is preloaded in the "Correo electronico" field
I type the "<Password>" in the "Contrasena" field
I type the "<PasswordConfirmation>" in the "Confirmar contrasena" field
I click on the "Siguiente" button
Loads the view "Cuentanos un poco mas de ti" social enrollment Step 2
The "<firstName>" is preloaded in the "Nombre" field and "<lastName>" in the "Apellido" field
I select the "<residenceCountry>" from the "Pais de residencia" dropdown
I select the birth date "<month>","<day>","<year>" in the dropdowns
I type the "numberID" in the "Identificador Nacional" field
I select the "<issuingCountry>" in the "Pais emisor" dropdown
I check the "termsAndConditions" checkbox
I check the "privacypolicies" checkbox
I validate that there is no mistake in the information entered in the fields
I click on the "Afiliate a Lifemiles" button
Redirect to account/overview section
